Now if your company has a very, very big budget

107
00:05:44,271 --> 00:05:45,947
you can use this product

108
00:05:45,947 --> 00:05:48,459
that McKinsey, Boston Consulting Group,

109
00:05:48,459 --> 00:05:50,886
and other top consulting firms use.

110
00:05:50,886 --> 00:05:55,357
Consultants are paid to analyze data and help companies.

111
00:05:55,357 --> 00:05:57,422
Quite often, they use data

