Alternatively, if you are giving a presentation

121
00:07:37,460 --> 00:07:40,393
on a company that is publicly traded

122
00:07:40,393 --> 00:07:43,483
you can go to whatever government website

123
00:07:43,483 --> 00:07:47,650
these companies have to list financial data at by law.

124
00:07:48,510 --> 00:07:52,026
For example, let's say you're giving a presentation

125
00:07:52,026 --> 00:07:54,917
on the future of the auto market and which companies

126
