or data-oriented slides that you didn't include

245
00:14:26,592 --> 00:14:29,175
or you have as extra resources.

246
00:14:31,015 --> 00:14:32,617
Here's an example here.

247
00:14:32,617 --> 00:14:34,921
You can right-click on, for example, PowerPoint,

248
00:14:34,921 --> 00:14:36,717
and go to a bunch of slides later on

249
00:14:36,717 --> 00:14:38,887
and it will make you look like a million bucks.

250
00:14:38,887 --> 00:14:41,757
Don't worry if that sounds a little bit confusing right now

251
00:14:41,757 --> 00:14:45,906
because I'm going to cover exactly how to do this,

